== Availability ==
Like other Xenon ships, it is possible to see the ship available for "sale" at Xenon shipyards, but it is never possible to actually land and purchase them, so the I must be boarded to capture.

== Suggested Roles==

If you manage to capture a Xenon I, you have one of the strongest M2+ destroyers in your hands.  Like other Xenon ships, it is frequently more useful in player hands than the AI, but it is deadly no matter its pilot.

